{
  "prompt": "A trippy, occult, psychedelic funeral scene with abstract symbolism. The setting features a surreal, dreamlike landscape with glowing colors, sacred geometry patterns, otherworldly crows or ravens, candles floating in air, and veiled figures in ritual garments. The central area should have a mysterious, glowing void or portal with dark purple and crimson hues, framed by vines or tendrils of light. The style should be highly artistic, mystical, and ethereal — blending DMT-style visuals with occult and funeral themes. Leave space in the center for inserting a female figure (Lilith).",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "An abstract psychedelic image representing the essence of 'Veyron Logos'—a fusion of celestial geometry, serpent fire, electric thunder, and deep shadow. The scene swirls with radiant sigils, reversed seraphic wings made of light, and crystalline bone-like structures emerging from the void. Vortexes of purple, indigo, silver, and gold spiral around a central unseen force. No human figures are present, only mythic symbolic elements evoking occult rebirth, divine rebellion, and multidimensional power.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "A vibrant, psychedelic abstract artwork in bold magenta and electric blue, inspired by Los Angeles floral design, Jimi Hendrix album art, Grateful Dead poster style, and infused with the mythic energy of Veyron Logos. Swirling flower patterns explode like sound waves across the canvas, with radiant spirals, paisley shapes, flame motifs, and alchemical sigils subtly integrated throughout. The background pulses with cosmic energy and radiant color gradients, evoking a dreamlike, spiritual rock-and-roll dimension.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}
